            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">✅ Phase 2: Extract Functions from Schema Branch (COMPLETE - Prompts 1-2)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                ✅ Pulled complete source code for all 9 functions from git schema branch with full verification. All functions extracted and ready for controller integration.
            </p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Functions to Extract:</strong></p>
            
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-radius: 3px; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;"><strong>Core Functions (3):</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>sync_table_to_result()</strong> [schema:3316-3383] - Sync DB table fields to Result file</li>
                    <li><strong>sync_result_to_table()</strong> [schema:3384-3451] - Sync Result file fields to DB table</li>
                    <li><strong>create_result_from_table()</strong> [schema:3811-3850+] - Generate Result file from DB table</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-radius: 3px; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;"><strong>Helper Functions (6):</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>get_table_field_info()</strong> [schema:3452-3567] - Get DB field definitions</li>
                    <li><strong>get_result_field_info()</strong> [schema:3568-3681] - Get Result file field definitions</li>
                    <li><strong>update_result_field_from_table()</strong> [schema:3682-3790] - Update Result field from DB</li>
                    <li><strong>update_table_field_from_result()</strong> [schema:3791-3810] - Update DB field from Result</li>
                    <li><strong>generate_result_file()</strong> [schema:3094-3121] - Create Result file structure</li>
                    <li><strong>generate_result_file_content()</strong> [schema:3122-3315] - Generate Result file content</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">✅ Phase 3: Create Controller Submodule (COMPLETE - Prompt 3)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                ✅ Created <strong>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Controller/Admin/SchemaComparison.pm</strong> (738 lines) with Moose boilerplate, 3 core action methods, 10 helper methods, lazy builder patterns, and logging integration. Syntax validation passed.
            </p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">✅ Phase 4: Template Merge (COMPLETE - Prompt 4)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                ✅ Updated <strong>Comserv/root/admin/schema_compare.tt</strong> to call new controller routes (/schema-comparison/*). Fixed 3 JavaScript endpoint references in createResultFromTable(), syncTableToResult(), and syncResultToTable() functions.
            </p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">✅ Phase 5: Validation & Testing (COMPLETE - Prompt 4)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                ✅ Syntax validation passed. Module loads successfully within Comserv application context with all dependencies resolved. Ready for manual endpoint testing.
            </p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">✅ Phase 6: Completion Logging (COMPLETE - Prompt 4)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                ✅ Updated prompts_log.yaml with Phase 4-5 results, updated SchemaCompareRecoveryPlan.tt status to COMPLETE. All 6 phases documented with execution details and file references.
            </p>
