            <h2 id="critical-dependencies" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Critical Dependencies & Notes</h2>

            <div style="background: var(--info-color, #d1ecf1); border-left: 4px solid var(--info-border, #17a2b8); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 3px;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;"><strong>⚠️ Bidirectional Sync Requirements:</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>DB→Result: Table fields sync to Result file columns</li>
                    <li>Result→DB: Result file columns sync to table fields</li>
                    <li>Create: Generate Result file from table (one-way, new file)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Dependency Chain</h3>
            <pre style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-radius: 3px; color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; overflow-x: auto;">
create_result_from_table()
  ├─ generate_result_file()
  │  └─ generate_result_file_content()
  └─ (needs output path)

sync_table_to_result()
  ├─ get_table_field_info()
  └─ update_result_field_from_table()

sync_result_to_table()
  ├─ get_result_field_info()
  └─ update_table_field_from_result()
            </pre>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">DBI Pattern Notes</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Main branch:</strong> Uses Moose lazy builder _build_db_config()</li>
                <li><strong>Schema branch:</strong> Used direct global my $config = decode_json(...)</li>
                <li><strong>Action:</strong> Keep main branch pattern, ensure schema branch functions work with it</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Template Compatibility</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Schema branch:</strong> Uses HTML &lt;table&gt; elements</li>
                <li><strong>Main branch:</strong> Uses Bootstrap containers/divs</li>
                <li><strong>Action:</strong> Use tables for now, can refactor to containers/Bootstrap later</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

